column1: Supplemental Data Set 4. Molar fractions (mol%) of proteins in Col-0 samples grown in the five thermocycles. The data set also includes downloaded responses for transcripts of the corresponding genes after transfer from 20°C to 17, 14, 12, 10 or 8°C for 1 hour or 1 day (Usadel et al., 2008b) and (where significant) the response of the corresponding genes to overexpression of CBF2 (Vogel et al., 2005).
